name: Paladin Fashion
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:

https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi

Paladin Fashion

We are warriors, born from the light
An army for freedom, defenders of life

At night, high up in the heavens we fight
Faster than lightning we strike
Like fires that rip through the night
Surrounded by light

Raging thunder in the skies
Time has come to sacrifice

Those of you that recognize the lyrics of this song and are emboldened by its lyrics, welcome.

Those of you that do not, fear not brothers you will be put up to speed quite easily.

It's time to make your inner light SHINE!

Download this LoRA, for the light!

Trigger words

Paladin, paladin_glam, paladin armor

Use them!
